nodes.text: Wookiee World Horror Witness! was a TriNebulon News feature released in 41 ABY to HoloNet channels. It featured Lieutenant Tirs Maladane of the Imperial II-class Star Destroyer Anakin Solo recounting the events of the Battle of Kashyyyk during the Second Galactic Civil War, in which the forests of Kashyyyk were set ablaze by the turbolaser guns of the Anakin Solo.
